      "name": "Cybernetic Feedback",
      "abstract": "Cybernetic feedback connects control, communication, systems theory, generative art, machine listening, adaptive interfaces and runtime governance.",
      "description": "Cybernetic feedback is the circulation of information about a system's state back into the system so that behavior can be regulated, adapted or transformed.",
